rows.label: qst003602_msg0001
rows.name:
What do you want with a Mopopo
who doesn't want to work, mo?

rows.label: qst003602_msg0002
rows.name:
...Oh, it's about
Hula-san's package, mo.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0003
rows.name: What she ordered is right here, mo.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0004
rows.name: But I'm not delivering it, mo.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0005
rows.name:
After Morph left, they banned
the service fee we used to add
on for deliveries to Gula, mo.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0006
rows.name:
It's all because those Militia Corps
people cracked down on it, mo.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0007
rows.name:
I only did that boring
delivery job because I got
a lot of money for it.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0008
rows.name: I don't want to do it anymore, mo.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0009
rows.name: Did Hula-san ask you to come, mo?

rows.label: qst003602_msg0010
rows.name:
Are you heading back to
where Hula-san is, mo?

rows.label: qst003602_msg0011
rows.name: Then it's settled, mo.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0012
rows.name:
You can take the package
I'm not delivering, mo.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0013
rows.name:
Mopopo may not want to work,
but my brain is still working,
mo! Praise me, mo!

rows.label: qst003602_msg0014
rows.name:
It's a shame I won't get to taste
the Ama-Ama Uinna I used to eat
while delivering packages, but...

rows.label: qst003602_msg0015
rows.name:
Mopopo doesn't want to
do pointless labor, mo.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0016
rows.name:
Well, you can tell Hula-san that
depending on the conditions, I
might take the job again, mo.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0017
rows.name: Well then, I'm counting on you, mo.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0101
rows.name:
Ama-Ama Uinna... Gula Amamitsu
Tea... Ruska Dumplings...

rows.label: qst003602_msg0102
rows.name:
I don't want to work, but I do
want to eat Gulan food, mo.

rows.label: qst003602_msg0103
rows.name:
I wonder if some will fall
from the sky, mo...?
